            <title><![CDATA[Danganronpa 2×2 announced for PS5, Xbox Series, Switch 2, Switch, and PC]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/09/danganronpa-2x2-announced-for-ps5-xbox-series-switch-2-switch-and-pc</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/danganronpa-2%C3%972-announced-for-ps5-xbox-series-switch-2-switch-and-pc.1296027/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div><p>Publisher <a title="Companies > Spike Chunsoft [891 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/kadokawa-corporation/spike-chunsoft">Spike Chunsoft</a> and developer <a title="Companies > Gemdrops [51 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/gemdrops">Gemdrops</a> has announced <em><a title="Games > Danganronpa 2: Goodbye Despair [16 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/danganronpa-2-goodbye-despair">Danganronpa 2: Goodbye Despair</a></em> remake <em><a title="Games > Danganronpa 2x2" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/danganronpa-2x2">Danganronpa 2×2</a></em> for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [10,349 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [7,890 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch 2 [403 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch-2">Switch 2</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch [17,653 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [24,219 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> (Steam). It will launch in 2026. <span id="more-991644"></span></p><p>Here is an overview of the game, via Spike Chunsoft:</p><blockquote><p><strong>About</strong></p><p>The latest installment in the high-speed detective <a title="Genres > Action [3,029 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/action">action</a> <em><a title="Series > Danganronpa [7 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/series/danganronpa">Danganronpa</a></em> series! Reveal the truth by shooting down contradictions in a Class Trial and uncover the culprit of a murder.</p><p>A new killing game begins in the same setting and with the same characters as <em>Danganronpa 2: Goodbye Despair</em>.</p><p>The original scenario from <em>Danganronpa 2: Goodbye Despair</em>, with revamped visuals and presentation for modern consoles, is also included.</p><!-- AD: content -->
        <p><strong>New Scenario</strong></p><p>A brand-new scenario with different victims, culprits, and tricks!</p><p>This new scenario contains just as much gameplay as the original.</p><p><strong>Staff</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Planning and Production:</strong> Spike Chunsoft Co., Ltd.</li><li><strong>Developer:</strong> Gemdrops, Inc.</li><li><strong>Supervision:</strong> Kazutaka Kodaka (<a title="Companies > Too Kyo Games [84 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/too-kyo-games">Too Kyo Games</a>)</li><li><strong>Original Concept and Trick Ideas:</strong> Takekuni Kitayama, Kazutaka Kodaka</li><li><strong>Scenario:</strong> Yoichiro Koizumi (Too Kyo Games)</li><li><strong>Sound:</strong> <a title="Companies > Mas [1 article]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/mas">Mas</a>afumi Takada, Jun Fukuda (Too Kyo Games)</li><li><strong>Design:</strong> Rui Komatsuzaki (Too Kyo Games)</li></ul></blockquote><p>Watch the announcement trailer below. Visit the official website <a href="https://www.danganronpa.com/2x2/en/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">here</a>.</p><h2><span>Announce Trailer</span></h2><p><strong>Japanese</strong></p><p><iframe title="『ダンガンロンパ２×２』ティザートレーラー" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/CVWI5laS1fc?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p></div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/09/danganronpa-2x2-announced-for-ps5-xbox-series-switch-2-switch-and-pc]]></content:encoded>
